    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "High\nfever\n(at least 102.2) for minimum of 2 weeks\nFaint erythematous macular coalescing\nrash\non the trunk, palms, soles\nArthritis (usually polyarticular)\nMay also have\nhepatosplenomegaly\n,\nlymphadenopathy\n, pleuritis,\npericardial effusion",
